UID:c9fc7f8ed98bfec88c339b864a8af7f8@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:Please note the May 13th Strahl Lake Hike meets AT Strahl Lake
 ! The paper version of the schedule incorrectly lists the Nature Center as
  the starting location. Join a park naturalist for a guided hike of Trail 
 6 around Lake Strahl! Hear about the history of the lake\, the surrounding
  Strahl Valley\, and learn about the animals that make it their home. The 
 section of Trail 6 around Lake Strahl is considered easy to moderate. It h
 as some short staircases\, uneven surfaces\, and wet spots. The trail is l
 ess than a mile and will take about 45 minutes to complete.
LOCATION:Brown County State Park\, Lake Strahl parking lot\, 1405 S.R. 46 
 W\, Nashville\, IN 
URL:https://on.in.gov/browncountysp
