DESCRIPTION:Come join the Brown County State Park naturalists\, O&#39\;Ban
 non Woods State Park naturalists\, and the Hoosier Herptological Society f
 or an exciting Saturday! We have walk up displays of reptiles all day\, wi
 th opportunities for learning\, petting\, and pictures! Special presentati
 ons occur at the top of every hour. We also have some snake arts and craft
 s to take with you! 11am: Earth&#39\;s Most Venomous Snakes 12pm: Snake Me
 et and Greet 1pm: Searching for Hidden Herps 2pm: Timber! Understanding th
 e Timber Rattlesnake 3pm: Snakes of Indiana 4pm: Rattlesnake Walk 5pm: Sna
 ke Meet and Greet
