DESCRIPTION:Join a park naturalist for a guided night hike around Lake Ogl
 e! The Full Moon is the brightest night of the month\, leading to excellen
 t views of the lake. Learn about July&#39\;s full moon\, the Buck Moon. Tr
 ail 7 is rated moderate\, but should be considered rugged in the dark. The
